  <article id="welcomeParaph">
    <p>Welcome to Shelf Indulgence's website! Please take a few minutes to browse
    around and learn about us. Shelf Indulgence is a used book store in Madison
    that strives to spread a love of books and reading throughout the
    community.</p> <p>We are hoping to have an author signing soon, so come
    back and check our website often to hear the latest and become a friend of
    Shelf Indulgence by filling out our new frind form on the Become a Frind
    page to get out newsletter so you can hear about the latest and greatest
    goings on here at Shelf Indulgence.</p> <p>The staff of Shelf Indulgence
    are thinking of starting a tea and buiscuits and books club or event, so if
    you would like us to work toward making that happen, feel free to contact
    us and let us know if that is something in which our patrons would enjoy
    participating.</p>
